comments: Biyombo (CHA) extends two hands into Griffin (DET) and dislodges him from his legal picking position.
Galloway (DET) makes incidental contact with Graham (CHA)  during the drive.
Kennard (DET) extends his forearm into Biyombo's (CHA) back and affects his ability to rebound.
Washington (CHA) legally jumps alongside Rose (DET) during his driving shot attempt and makes clean contact with the ball.  Batum (CHA) then cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Drummond (DET) makes marginal contact with his lower body with Graham (CHA) but does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Biyombo (CHA) makes contact with the ball as he and Drummond (DET) attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Drummond (DET) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Biyombo (CHA).  He has his arms extended, but the contact is marginal.
Washington (CHA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of Galloway (DET).
Biyombo (CHA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of Rose (DET),
Griffin (DET) briefly grasps Biyombo's (CHA) arm, but the contact is marginal.
Griffin (DET) makes marginal contact with Biyombo (CHA) as he attempts to retrieve the loose ball.
During the inbound play, Biyombo (CHA) wraps Drummond (DET) and affects his FOM.
Batum (CHA) commits a take foul on Rose (DET).
Drummond (DET) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of Batum (CHA).
